{"tid":332551,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"打風最好留係屋企整野食~ 香蕉朱古力蛋糕","createTime":"2017-07-23T05:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T06:56:19.000Z","uid":4548,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbb95e9b9f4379708f66e9ffdfd992ca1a820b6","tid":332551,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"都幾易整，大概整咗個零鐘 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/131933_c0a45622543ae1fddc893bcc92778917.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F131933_c0a45622543ae1fddc893bcc92778917.jpg&h=f5c716de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/131938_a775af5c1dcfecdc05d90e3312754154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F131938_a775af5c1dcfecdc05d90e3312754154.jpg&h=e0e9768b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整咗一個圓形，一個長方形 再加幾個紙杯裝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n切開就係咁。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/132521_02129b1a5472c275c2c00130ec4de4e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F132521_02129b1a5472c275c2c00130ec4de4e8.jpg&h=95385b4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗完好香好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n屋企個個都食咗兩舊，表示好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n不過都覺得有啲地方可以改進下，如果你地整可以注意一下。 <br />\n<br />\n1.食譜中糖嘅份量，我已經落少咗20g 都仲係頗甜，唔鐘意太甜嘅巴絲可以再落少d ~ <br />\n<br />\n2.佢聲稱焗20~30 mins ， 但焗完都未熟透。然後再焗多10分鐘 ，唔知係咪朱古力粒放太多 所以中間會多咗融融地嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n3.加多d 核桃粒應該會再正d <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7271f34287cfc2052054fea295b2900b453355","tid":332551,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"055bf88a0297e964ee2ada5387d9ef2de87ea15d","tid":332551,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"我跟呢個整 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/daydaycooker/videos/1581660701883998/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdaydaycooker%2Fvideos%2F1581660701883998%2F&d=T8Rla5ECJQFl2tgwsLfgl%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=aff94942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/daydaycooker/videos/1581660701883998/</a>"},{"pid":"c7ef34649fa8523033d5230eab3a41db428c7ca7","tid":332551,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"燶"},{"pid":"7260af5f02a11799d6d06d553541863a38ad0c46","tid":332551,"uid":74981,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>喺</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n鐘意<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>鍾意</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XbZCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXbZCs.png&h=90b16d4b&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，冇人覺得你好醒wo肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbacafe7010eecfe3b448f5b3f8d6652c635259","tid":332551,"uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"第一眼仲以為係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c492d2b6b2907d91f861e3006f70f05133dbdba","tid":332551,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一眼仲以為係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁話佢啦 好好食㗎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm