kquote>我好鍾意食香蕉味嘅甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾好呀 你可以試下整 <br />\n係上面灑啲糖霜 可能會靚仔啲"},{"pid":"667a154a360cb4d45f2bfcbf61f8dcde069dd0d2","tid":332551,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好黑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朱古力係咁 我都沒計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9de1962491c2358d9b1168baa56ea330079078a","tid":332551,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好鍾意食香蕉味嘅甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾好呀 你可以試下整 <br />\n係上面灑啲糖霜 可能會靚仔啲</blockquote><br />\n唔駛灑糖霜整色整水啦，睇你嘅製成品好有啱啱出爐好新鮮嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4024f00df9cce6ecaf8ec546a2e98c0ef60549be","tid":332551,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89629c1d00236b60d04086fc239cee7592c8cd6b","tid":332551,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>喺</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n鐘意<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>鍾意</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XbZCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXbZCs.png&h=90b16d4b&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，冇人覺得你好醒wo肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwo你老母<br />\n溫下書先講嘢啦冇學識冇文化冇修養嘅死肥鳩</blockquote><br />\n一個無受過教育既柒頭肥鳩幻想自己係老師，笑死人咩on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文你又唔敢講，中文又唔識多隻，咪撚成日掛住上嚟叫春同煮垃圾啦，增值自己好撚過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你淨係閱讀障礙都已經連自我增值都無能為力啦垃圾，(係你自己係你個comment度自爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)老師wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老閪你就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b568d80d1ea9ac5fef4fcc6856ffd85f49c0a7d","tid":332551,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"見到狗狗同絲絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608e67581dbf4ba358d98833c0d8c655a0fa8dd3","tid":332551,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到狗狗同絲絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a078607730949cddb3c7370889d2a1fed2233d9","tid":332551,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"等我食完先話你知好唔好食"}]}